            <h2>Introduction to Salon & Barbershop Valuation</h2>
            <p>The beauty industry is experiencing unprecedented growth, with the global beauty services market valued at over $190 billion in 2025. <strong>Salon and barbershop valuation</strong> requires specialized knowledge of service-based revenue models, client retention patterns, and industry-specific metrics that traditional business valuations often overlook.</p>
