            </div>
            <div class="faq-item" style="background: #f8f9fa; border-left: 4px solid #3498db; padding: 20px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0;">
                <h4>How is salon valuation different from other businesses?</h4>
                <p>Salon valuations focus heavily on service-based metrics like client retention rates, average service tickets, and chair utilization. The personal service nature, stylist dependencies, and licensing requirements make beauty businesses unique from product-based companies.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item" style="background: #f8f9fa; border-left: 4px solid #3498db; padding: 20px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0;">
